			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_65024963" name="comment_link_65024963" href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23555625&amp;cid=65024963" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(65024963)" >Re:Counterproductive regulations?</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_65024963" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 65024963); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
