			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_65024963">		
		on Thursday December 19, 2024 @09:09AM (<span class="ind"></span><a rel="nofollow" href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23555625&amp;cid=65024963">#65024963</a>)
